'P2'     'OPEN'    'BHP'   5*   4000 /
'P3'     'OPEN'    'BHP'   5*   4000 /
-- Producers are controlled at BHP = 4000 psi.

Injector:
pushes water in at rate = 5000
creates pressure in reservoir
Producers (P1–P4):
are set to BHP = 4000 psi
this is a fixed pressure boundary
